      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 wide-body aesthetic. This specimen features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six M96/03 powerplant, delivering 315 hp through a G96/31 six-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the IMS bearing has been addressed with an LN Engineering ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal (RMS) remains bone dry. The suspension retains its factory-tuned poise with Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, while the braking system utilizes the Turbo-spec four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. The Arctic Silver Metallic paint shows zero signs of oxidation or clear-coat failure, and the interior's Full Leather supple seating is free of bolster wear or UV damage. Service records are comprehensive, documenting meticulous fluid intervals and a recent clutch replacement. This is a collector-grade 996 for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
